reviews.comment: The app is the most accurate out of all the others and if you could think of more to add for free will be awesome! And the horoscopes still need fixing please help! reviews.title: Easy,  Accurate & Fun
reviews.comment: I don\'t routinely leave feedback on apps but this one is the exception to the rule.   Excellent mini reports with pinpoint accuracy, it is worth paying for so just the fact that it is free makes it more than worth the download.  Now just expand on the reports to include the outer planets, houses and aspects on the astrology side and feel free to charge for it. I would pay in a heartbeat.

reviews.title: Stars and Numbers
reviews.comment: This is THE app to get if you\'re interested in astrology, horoscopes, and numerology.  Easy to set up and use.  Extended readings for day, week, month, and year for numerology and horoscopes (Western and Chinese).  Better color scheme choices would be nice, but that\'s my only criticism.  Love it!  ##Samsung Galaxy II Notebook##
